  <h1>What is recursion?</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jun 16, 2026</span><span>8 min read</span><span class="tag">#recursion</span><span class="tag">#concepts</span><span class="tag">#functional</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?w=1200&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Colourful syntax-highlighted source code on a dark screen" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
